[{"_path":"/legacy-articles/2017-01-23-aoe-ii-time-of-upgrade-ages","_dir":"legacy-articles","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"世紀帝國 II 系列：時代升級所需時間","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://blog.fntsr.tw/articles/613/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"世紀帝國 II 系列：時代升級所需時間 - 深藏若虛"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"網路上多是描述幾分點擊封建、幾分要升上城堡時代，倒是沒特別說升級時代需要多少時間。所以在這邊簡短紀錄一下。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"一般文明"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一般文明"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"升級封建時代：2 分 10 秒"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"升級城堡時代：2 分 40 秒"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"升級帝王時代：3 分 10 秒"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"所以若要在 18 分以前升上城堡時代，大約 15:20 前就要點升級了。另外在主流的 N + 2 打法，也就是升上封建後，訓練兩隻村民再升城堡，中間的時間就拿來建造需要升級城堡時代的兩棟建築物，訓練一隻村民需要 25 秒，所以這中間大約就是 50 秒的時間，那也就是說需要 14:30 升上封建時代，再往前推就是 11:20 前要點升級封建時代。整體算下來來從點擊升級封建時代到升級完城堡時代所需的時間約 5 分 40 秒，如果要在 16 分升城，那最慢就是要在 10:20 要有辦法點升封了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"code":"升城所需時間 = 130 + 25 * 2 + 160 = 340 (秒)\n"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"升城所需時間 = 130 + 25 * 2 + 160 = 340 (秒)\n"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要在 14:00 升上城堡，需在 08:20 時點擊封建時代"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要在 15:00 升上城堡，需在 09:20 時點擊封建時代"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要在 16:00 升上城堡，需在 10:20 時點擊封建時代"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要在 17:00 升上城堡，需在 11:20 時點擊封建時代"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要在 18:00 升上城堡，需在 12:20 時點擊封建時代"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"所以要做升城練習的第一步，就是想辦法在你需要點擊封建時代的那個時間點，訓練出 N 隻村民，並擁有 500 食物了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"馬來西亞"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"馬來西亞"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"馬來西亞的種族特性為「Advancing to Ages takes only 60% of the usual time」，字面上的意思就是他在升級時代的速度，只需正常時間的 60%。"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"^1"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"code":"馬來西亞升級時代所需時間 = 原本升級所需時間 * 0.6\n"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"馬來西亞升級時代所需時間 = 原本升級所需時間 * 0.6\n"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"升級封建時代：1 分 18 秒 (快 52 秒)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"升級城堡時代：1 分 36 秒 (快 64 秒，累計快 116 秒)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"升級帝王時代：1 分 54 秒 (快 76 秒，累計快 192 秒)"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"承上面 N+2 打法的公式，整體算下來，馬來西亞從點擊升級封建時代到升級完城堡時代所需的時間約 3 分 44 秒。如果要在 16 分升城，那最慢只要在 12:16 秒有辦法點升封就可以了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"code":"升城所需時間 = 78 + 25 * 2 + 96 = 224 (秒)\n"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"升城所需時間 = 78 + 25 * 2 + 96 = 224 (秒)\n"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要在 12:00 升上城堡，需在 08:16 時點擊封建時代"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要在 13:00 升上城堡，需在 09:16 時點擊封建時代"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要在 14:00 升上城堡，需在 10:16 時點擊封建時代"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要在 15:00 升上城堡，需在 11:16 時點擊封建時代"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要在 16:00 升上城堡，需在 12:16 時點擊封建時代"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要在 17:00 升上城堡，需在 13:16 時點擊封建時代"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要在 18:00 升上城堡，需在 14:16 時點擊封建時代"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"值得注意的是，儘管馬來西亞在升級時代速度上有著顯著的優勢，但在升級時代之間，因為時間變少了，所以採集資源的數量變少了，進而在封建時代時，可能會無法在訓練兩隻村民的 50 秒內，存夠能升城堡的資源量，導致節奏被打亂。因此建議馬來西亞在升級封建時代的時間，可以比平時慢 50 秒，也就是多兩隻村民訓練時間，不但避免經濟卡住，又能增加經濟優勢。最後再利用升城速度的優勢，進行城快攻勢。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1"}]},{"type":"text","value":": 馬來西亞在種族加成部分，升級時代的加速加成在 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://ageofempires.wikia.com/wiki/Malay","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Wikia"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 裡的說明是正確的數據「原本的 60%」，但在遊戲裡科技樹裡似乎還是寫「快 80%」，這個「快 80%」不知是否另有意義，還是純粹數據沒有更新，不得而知。至少敝人實測的結果是「原本的 60%」沒錯。"}]}]},"title_en":"AOE II: Time of Upgrade Ages","slug":"aoe-ii-time-of-upgrade-ages","aliases":["世紀帝國 II 系列：時代升級所需時間","AOE II: Time of Upgrade Ages"],"created_at":"2017-01-23T16:49:49.000Z","published_at":null,"updated_at":null,"tags":["aoe"],"moc":["Games"],"_type":"markdown","_id":"garden:legacy-articles:2017-01-23-aoe-ii-time-of-upgrade-ages.md","_source":"garden","_file":"legacy-articles/2017-01-23-aoe-ii-time-of-upgrade-ages.md","_extension":"md"},{"_path":"/legacy-articles/2017-